Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:21.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Living through these meaningless days, I let out a sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:29.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I've lost sight of my true self
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:36.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Even if I strain my ears I can't hear your voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:43.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}So I keep walking trying to catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:50.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The things I couldn't tell you form into a chrysalis over time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:58.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,300)}Spreading wings, they take flight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:06.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The one, the one precious thing I'll never forget
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:13.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Someday, that warm emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:19.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I'll do what little I can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:28.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\c&H98ADF1&}Little by little, to get through to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.41,0:01:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tanuma was possessed by a demon.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.16,0:01:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And until we find all the pieces of the broken mirror,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it won't leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was worried about leaving him alone,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.46,0:01:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I decided to stay at his house.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.80,0:01:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the priest?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.88,0:01:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's on a business trip again.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.89,0:01:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tanuma kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a chestnut.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.98,0:02:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.06,0:02:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.23,0:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How many mirror pieces did we get this afternoon?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all. Can you see it?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.87,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.16,0:02:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just barely tell there's something there.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more careful with that.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.55,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you be more careful with Tanuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.26,0:02:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Gimme back my chestnut!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.89,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, gimme back my chestnut!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd feel much better if I were the one who was possessed.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The mirror went into my eye!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.98,0:02:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. It wants to become whole again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The pieces will resonate with one another,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.99,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and demand that you pick them up.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When you find them all, this will end.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.41,0:03:02.41,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Ref{\c&H025A07&}le{\c}ction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:02.41,title-shadow,,0,0,0,,{\blur7)}Ref{\c&H49539A&\4a&HFF&\blur4.5}le{\c\4a\blur7}ction
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.75,0:03:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Has this ever happened to you, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.58,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a demon ask you for something.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me started.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All the time?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master Nyanko{*Nyanko-sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.47,0:03:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.06,0:03:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't say no to anything a spirit asks him to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.31,0:03:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He ought to just tell them to buzz off.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't help it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.83,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tanuma...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's not him.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come here any more, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.85,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the dream of the demon that's possessing Tanuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.27,0:04:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I done something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.19,0:04:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just don't come here anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.61,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.50,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking into my dream, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.62,0:04:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the friend you're looking for?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.30,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That demon seemed to be sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you heal him with that mirror?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a terrible disease...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.77,0:04:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something... anything that can heal him?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.76,0:05:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you truly wish to heal him?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.43,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, there {\i1}is{\i0} something.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.10,0:05:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it won't be easy to get.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.37,0:05:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just rest!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.71,0:05:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll warm you up.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give you a hot bath,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.80,0:06:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can rest in our arms.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you persevere?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.73,0:06:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not here to take our mirror, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.32,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't!{your choice what to do here}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been deceived.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.66,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The hated sun will rise!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mirror will appear!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.58,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a way to cure your disease!{extend lead-out and transform to white if you wish, or fade}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.71,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it... happen again?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That sound was from the temple.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.34,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A thief... or not.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was broken from the outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.56,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The forest raccoons like to play tricks at this time of year.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.19,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew what he could see,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I could at least understand what he's trying to do...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to see?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can lend you my eyes
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in exchange for borrowing your body.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to see?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.01,0:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume can see this?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.74,0:09:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The hammer wielding demon from school is in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.16,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does Natsume see a world with stuff like this everywhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it, Tanuma?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon lent me her eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.19,0:09:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.57,0:09:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll break it and take it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.54,0:10:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let a weakling like you take my mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tanuma?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.22,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't show the demons to Tanuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.77,0:10:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you saved me, but don't put him through that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the mirror, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend's important to you, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.12,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma is my friend, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do anything more to him!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.33,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you possess me instead of Tanuma?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you look for the mirror,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so please, let Tanuma go.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.76,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the one who wanted to see spirits.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.22,0:11:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You never talk about them.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.31,0:11:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't need to, I suppose.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're so kind.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows that,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.24,0:11:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but he'll never understand unless you tell him.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll never understand something so important.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.45,0:11:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right beside you, but he doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.17,0:11:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend didn't tell me either.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.38,0:11:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He never told me...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that he was seriously ill.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He left me so that I wouldn't get sick, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.26,0:11:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I only heard the rumors on the wind.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.98,number-box,,0,0,0,,{\be1.5\c&H2412C9&\fscx46\fscy45\pos(1760,1046)}\h
Dialogue: 2,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.98,number,,0,0,0,,{\be1.5\fay-0.14\fscx46\fscy47\c&H2412C9&\pos(1762,1048)}3
