Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.98,titlename-blur,,0,0,0,,{\p1\blur20\pos(1238,1079)}m 0 0 s 1350 0 1350 150 0 150 c
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.28,0:11:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he had told me,\N I couldn't have done anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.66,0:12:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But after my desperate search, I finally found it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The mirror that can purge his illness.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.38,0:12:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is find him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.84,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find the pieces of the mirror soon!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Or he'll...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find the mirror before it's too late.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.10,0:12:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, child of man.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.89,0:12:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's all I can do to stay in his body.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, child of man.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Yatsuhara for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.24,0:12:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty sad that a weak demon like that could get onto the temple grounds.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.33,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master Nyanko{*Nyanko-sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in serious trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.96,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching to see who that hammer guy was.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.46,0:12:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But she got rid of it before I could help.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.55,0:13:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go to bed, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look after things.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.47,0:13:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to spend any more time on this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finishing it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, {*}Master{Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, carry Tanuma to his bed.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.49,0:13:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.49,0:13:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to clean up the broken window.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me big time for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.12,0:13:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna take more than a meat bun from Nanatsujiya!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.54,0:13:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to pay Tanuma for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.38,0:13:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavy!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too heavy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on a diet!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Get slim!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really remember,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.52,0:13:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think something incredible came out of my mouth.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.61,0:13:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you eat?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.86,0:13:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that kind.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Natsume{*-kun}, here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.66,0:14:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I made this talisman based on some books I found in my house.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it'll help,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but not being able to do anything bothers me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.83,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it's not much, but I want you to take it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.63,0:14:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taki.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.01,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you stay up all night making it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I didn't go that far.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You get bags under your eyes really easily.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.06,0:14:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can get better at sewing soon...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the problem's your aesthetic sense, not your sewing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.19,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to be mean,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give you the one I made for people who are possessed.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.90,0:14:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry... wait, you made one for me, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.16,0:14:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I could do.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it said to make it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to make it in the middle of the night, so I was pretty creeped out too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.13,0:14:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's finish this today.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.72,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Master Nyanko, by the way?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.93,0:15:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd look around the school by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:18.65,sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1251,450.666)\blur1.2\frz295.5\c&H303034&}Catnip
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.48,0:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure ya find that spirit's mirror pieces fast, 'kay?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.49,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.03,0:15:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that the fragments would merge with things that shine, didn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.26,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain's going away.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.05,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to check all the mirrors we can find.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have stay after school to do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.73,0:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there demons here, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.86,0:16:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, small ones.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Want to see them?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.95,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Natsume sees these things everyday?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.21,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.00,0:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, the stuff you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look for the other pieces.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see them.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a nice mirror, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody must've put a lot of work into making it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a name on it somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a terrible excuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.38,0:17:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We've checked every mirror in school.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What else is there that can shine?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see something shining really brightly!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's shining.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Around here, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.62,0:17:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It still hurts.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.58,0:17:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.54,0:17:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taki.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll get you a towel.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.68,0:17:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tanuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's possessed.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm helping myself, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.19,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You go through this a lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about not talking about it much.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.11,0:18:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to talk about being scared or uneasy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kiddos.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.88,0:18:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a raccoon! Wait, it's just Ponta.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.09,0:18:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.05,0:18:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, are you carrying something?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're as powerful as I am,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.27,0:18:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,finding the fragments is as easy as finding hay in a haystack!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mister Madara{*Madara-sama}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mister Madara{*Madara-sama}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mister Madara{*Madara-sama}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.41,0:19:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this seriously already!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hay in a haystack...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds really impressive,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.88,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't actually mean anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, kid?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take this and go.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.98,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.53,0:19:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want that mirror!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.70,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the power!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.99,0:19:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.62,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't give you this mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.43,0:20:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that could get rid of a disease.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.19,0:20:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find my friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.58,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And get rid of his illness, and talk to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.71,0:20:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will she find him?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.43,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a serious illness.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.01,0:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's possible that her friend is already...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to look for him, that's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.65,0:20:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I need to yell at him,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or I'm not going to feel right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Farewell, child of man.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you have the chance to speak \Nto someone from the heart,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}do not fear it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.60,0:21:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's a difficult thing to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.60,0:21:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why it's rare, \Nand why you sometimes fail.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.15,0:21:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, the Tanuma Possession Incident ended, somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.16,0:21:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So she's gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to tell Taki.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.04,0:21:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I made you guys worry so much,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.83,0:21:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was kind of fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see what you saw,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.71,0:22:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was able to talk to that demon.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.18,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you talk to her about?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't tell you anything weird, did she?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You really go through a lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.44,0:22:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.69,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not all bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.28,0:22:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.36,0:22:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.20,0:22:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.25,0:24:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If that person hadn't come to see me back then, I'd...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.09,0:24:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the lonely ones. They're fun to watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume, where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time somebody asked me to go with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.01,0:24:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go with strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:41.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Lining up the sparks of warmth I've lost one by one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:49.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Coming to the rainbow-colored pieces of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:54.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I crack a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:08.58,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Not even knowing how to make memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:16.25,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even when we took things too fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:24.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We were only going with the flow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:31.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}No matter where I go, even after this darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:37.52,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}How many times must I say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:44.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Shining with the flame of a young heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:50.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Those faraway pieces of you
